title: [GRIFFIN-11] Enable accuracy measurement for batch mode
body:
[GRIFFIN-11]
Accuracy measurement for batch mode.

**Supporting**:
- hive data and avro file.
- simple calculation and exactly match function for ESL description.

**Not supporting**:
- param validation yet.
- condition filter expression before mapping match.
- sampling of data.
- persist data cleaner.
- more compare rule for mapping match.
- some group data feature for a batch of data.
